        "jsCode": "const total = Number($json.Total ?? 0);\nconst limit = 1000;\nconst pages = Math.max(1, Math.ceil(total / limit));\nreturn Array.from({ length: pages }, (_, i) => ({\n  json: { offset: i * limit, pageLimit: limit }\n}));"
